org.modelio.gproject.fragment

Class FragmentMigrationNeededException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • org.modelio.gproject.fragment.FragmentMigrationNeededException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class FragmentMigrationNeededException
extends Exception
    Indicates that a fragment needs to be migrated because the metamodel is outdated.

    Throw when mounting fragment and set as fragment down cause.

    See Also:
